000Z","msg":"轉食電子煙幫唔幫倒手？<br />\n但好似話因為電子煙太新，關於煙嘅研究做左好多年先知有咩害處，電子煙嘅研究未夠，所以好多害處係未知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過，個肺有冇好左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2800025/【肺腺癌】女子食電子煙3年疑致肺腺癌%E3%80%80醫生：尼古丁電子煙致癌性極高\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2800025%2F%E3%80%90%E8%82%BA%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%A3%9F%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E7%85%993%E5%B9%B4%E7%96%91%E8%87%B4%E8%82%BA%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%25E3%2580%2580%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%A4%E4%B8%81%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E7%85%99%E8%87%B4%E7%99%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%A5%B5%E9%AB%98&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=fb7b24f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2800025/【肺腺癌】女子食電子煙3年疑致肺腺癌%E3%80%80醫生：尼古丁電子煙致癌性極高</a>"},{"pid":"961266b19a6fcfd078beacc41418fd79da83e9b0","tid":2319441,"uid":54328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry <br />\n我真係想戒的<br />\n但煙好似毒藥咁<br />\n無尼古丁上腦，心情會低落同生理上辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347957b0aa6054aa15f9af43cb5011c30f8c99cc","tid":2319441,"uid":164330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ebf9d385fddeb80fbb07b62f89a45c37c3041f8","tid":2319441,"uid":207762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"轉食電子煙幫唔幫倒手？<br />\n但好似話因為電子煙太新，關於煙嘅研究做左好多年先知有咩害處，電子煙嘅研究未夠，所以好多害處係未知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過，個肺有冇好左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"電子煙原本就係煙既替代品<br />\n9成煙民轉食電子煙後覺得比較健康<br />\n轉食電子煙係正確既選擇<br />\n<br />\n你想吸經由燃燒產出煙霧(N種致己知癌物)既成品煙<br />\n定係加熱煙油產出既水蒸氣<br />\n<br />\n正常有尼古丁既煙油會頂到煙癮<br />\n不過賣有丁煙油係犯法  但你要搵係會搵到的<br />\n<br />\n至於電子煙係咪有害過真煙<br />\n正常途徑買到既電子煙油成份為VG, PG, 香味劑, 尼古丁(可選)<br />\n以上成份都係food grade 貪平買來源or成份不明既煙油係玩命<br />\n唔敢講vape係健康 但一定冇真煙咁致命<br />\n<br />\n加上煙草係世上其中一樣最大工業 <br />\n比市民發現原來電子煙係好過真煙咪仆街囉<br />\n等於政府不斷話黑衫就係搞事破壞一樣<br />\n自己研究下電子煙會比較好<br />\n <br />\n關於電子煙傷肺既新聞<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ik2wCHDMZ7I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dik2wCHDMZ7I&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=398ec8ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ik2wCHDMZ7I</a><br />\n啲on9撚樣買非法/不明成份既煙彈/thc煙油食到出事<br />\n芳間新聞就似tvb咁斬頭斬尾 話電子煙有害過真煙 真係笑撚左<br />\n就等於有人渣車超速自抄死左 芳間就話渣車危險要禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660e7dcb94639452e155520ea49795b1da105c8c","tid":2319441,"uid":229074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab005c690cf5d7d93e9adc21e60fb3f4edc991b3","tid":2319441,"uid":81738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"咁水煙呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"水煙咪又係傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a953165f86ff67b642f9cbab7bf439cf149c7bf","tid":2319441,"uid":34962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"勸人戒就唔好屌 唔洗話佢知壞處 食果個清楚過你<br />\n<br />\n要代入下佢點解需要食先有用"},{"pid":"6d738fd86552f2c3f3423e6a372950e3ab417d68","tid":2319441,"uid":151143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"選擇嚟，想戒唔使勸，要勸嘅都唔荒會戒"},{"pid":"80d4b4c592baa7680bb291a2d76f6e5cb8caf522","tid":2319441,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"你唔食煙 我比你屌"},{"pid":"179435ffccc373404741983af103c082ab7ba524","tid":2319441,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"無煙無酒<br />\n唯有濕鳩"}]}